Run the specs (from this directory) like this to get nice output:

$ spec spec --format=nested --color --diff=c

results in output:

    A board like this:
      
      ........
      ........
      ........
      ...BW...
      ...WB...
      ........
      ........
      ........
      B
    
    should result in these legal moves: 
      
      ........
      ........
      ....0...
      ...BW0..
      ..0WB...
      ...0....
      ........
      ........'


